  "text": "In this section, we would like to relate nonsingular decomposition of σ p,q with the continued fraction of p/q as is done in [CITATION_1] . According to the cocycle property of the (normalized) Todd series, the (normalized) Todd series is decomposed into sum of those of nonsingular cones.",
